data.description: Welcome to this charming ranch-style home nestled in the Northside community. It boasts three cozy bedrooms and full bathroom. Newer paint and flooring. The plumbing and lighting have been modernized, ensuring both functionality and style. The kitchen has been recently updated with plenty of cabinetry, offering plenty of storage for all your culinary needs. The adjacent eat-in area provides a perfect spot for meals and gatherings. For those who love tinkering, the huge garage is a dream come true. Not only does it offer extended space for vehicles, but it also includes a workshop area, ideal for projects and hobbies. The backyard is fully fenced and backs the neighborhood school. This home is conveniently located close to all amenities, yet it offers a peaceful retreat from the hustle and bustle of city life. With central air conditioning, comfort is guaranteed year-round. Don't miss the opportunity to make this delightful home yours – it's a rare find that won't last long!
